    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p>Cause awareness and giving days are powerful themes upon which to launch social media and online fundraising campaigns. In addition to the international days listed below, see also <strong><a href=\"http://publicholidays.global/\">public holidays by country</a></strong>,\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/\">Days of the Year</a></strong>, and\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_commemorative_months\">Wikipedia\u2019s List of Commemorative Months</a></strong>.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2><strong>January</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>19: <a href=\"https://www.pointsoflight.org/mlk-jr-day-of-service/\">Martin Luther King, Jr. Day of Service</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#MLKDay<br />\n28: <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Data_Privacy_Day\">Data Privacy Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0 #DataPrivacyDay</strong></p>\n<h2><strong>February</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>2:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.worldwetlandsday.org/\">World Wetlands Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldWetlandsDay<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_Cancer_Day\"><br />\n</a>4:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.worldcancerday.org/\">World Cancer Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldCancerDay<br />\n</strong><strong>10: <a href=\"https://better-internet-for-kids.europa.eu/en/saferinternetday\">Safer Internet Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#SaferInternetDay<br />\n12: <a href=\"http://www.digitallearningday.org/\">Digital Learning Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#DigitalLearningDay<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldCancerDay\"><br />\n</a>13:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.unesco.org/en/days/world-radio\">World Radio Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldRadioDay<br />\n15: <a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/world-whale-day/\">World Whale Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldWhaleDay<br />\n</strong><strong>20:</strong>\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/social-justice-day\">World Day of Social Justice</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#SocialJusticeDay<br />\n24: <a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/world-spay-day/\">World Spay Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldSpayDay<br />\n</strong><strong>27: <a href=\"https://polarbearsinternational.org/get-involved/international-polar-bear-day\">International Polar Bear Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#PolarBearDay<br />\n27: <a href=\"https://worldngoday.org/\">World NGO Day</a> \u2014\u00a0#WorldNGODay<br />\n</strong><strong>28: <a href=\"https://www.rarediseaseday.org/\">Rare Disease Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#RareDiseaseDay<br />\n</strong></p>\n<h2><strong>March</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>3:\u00a0<a href=\"http://wildlifeday.org/\">World Wildlife Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldWildlifeDay<br />\n8:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.internationalwomensday.com/\">International Women\u2019s Day</a> \u2014 #IWD2026</strong><br />\n<strong>12: <a href=\"https://www.worldkidneyday.org/\">World Kidney\u00a0Day</a> \u2014\u00a0#WorldKidneyDay<br />\n18: <a href=\"https://www.awarenessdays.com/awareness-days-calendar/global-recycling-day-2024/\">Global Recycling Day</a> \u2014 #GlobalRecyclingDay<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/endracismday\"><br />\n</a>21:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.fao.org/international-day-of-forests/en/\">International Day of Forests</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldForestsDay<br />\n21:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.worlddownsyndromeday.org/\">World Down Syndrome Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldDownSyndromeDay<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23ForestsDay\"><br />\n</a>21:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.unesco.org/en/days/poetry\">World Poetry Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldPoetryDay<br />\n22:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/water-day\">World Water Day</a> \u2014\u00a0#WorldWaterDay</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldWaterDay&amp;src=typd\"><br />\n</a><strong>24:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.who.int/campaigns/world-tb-day\">World Tuberculosis Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldTBDay<br />\n28: <a href=\"http://www.earthhour.org/\">Earth Hour</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#EarthHour<br />\n</strong></p>\n<h2><strong>April</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>2:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/autism-day\">World Autism Awareness Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldAustismDay<br />\n7: <a href=\"https://www.who.int/campaigns/world-health-day\">World Health Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldHealthDay<br />\n12: <a href=\"https://www.good-deeds-day.org/\">Good Deeds Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#GoodDeedsDay</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldAutismDay&amp;src=typd\"><br />\n</a><strong>12: <a href=\"https://www.nationaldayarchives.com/day/international-day-for-street-children/\">International Day for Street Children</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><strong>#StreetChildrenDay<br />\n</strong><strong>15: <a href=\"https://www.unesco.org/en/days/world-art\">World Art Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldArtDay<br />\n</strong><strong>22: <a href=\"http://www.earthday.org/\">Earth Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><strong>#EarthDay</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23EarthDay&amp;src=typd\"><strong><br />\n</strong></a><strong>23:\u00a0<a href=\"https://nationaltoday.com/world-book-day/\">World Book Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldBookDay</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23EarthDay&amp;src=typd\"><br />\n</a><strong>25: <a href=\"https://www.who.int/campaigns/world-malaria-day\">World Malaria Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><strong>#WorldMalariaDay</strong><br />\n<strong>25:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/world-penguin-day/\">World Penguin Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldPenguinDay<br />\n30: <a href=\"http://jazzday.com/\">International Jazz Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#JazzDay<br />\n</strong></p>\n<h2><strong>May</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>3:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/press-freedom-day\">World Press Freedom Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldPressFreedomDay<br />\n<strong>9: <a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/fair-trade-day/\">World Fair Trade Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldFairTradeDay<br />\n9: <a href=\"https://www.migratorybirdday.org/\">World Migratory Bird Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldMigratoryBirdDay<br />\n10: <a href=\"https://www.lupus.org/lupus-awareness-month/world-lupus-day\">World Lupus Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldLupusDay<br />\n12: <a href=\"https://www.icn.ch/how-we-do-it/campaigns/international-nurses-day\">International Nurses Day</a>\u00a0\u2014 #NursesDay<br />\n15: <a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/endangered-species-day/\">Endangered Species Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#EndangeredSpeciesDay<br />\n</strong><strong>17: <a href=\"https://human-rights-channel.coe.int/idahotb-en.html\">International\u00a0Day\u00a0Against\u00a0Homophobia,\u00a0Transphobia,\u00a0Biphobia</a> \u2014\u00a0#IDAHOTB<br />\n</strong><strong>18: <a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/museum-day/\">International Museum Day</a>\u00a0\u2014 #MuseumDay<br />\n22:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.cbd.int/idb/\">International Day for Biological Diversity</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#BiologicalDiversityDay</strong><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/WorldTurtleDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>23:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.awarenessdays.com/awareness-days-calendar/world-turtle-day/\">World Turtle Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><strong>#WorldTurtleDay</strong><br />\n<strong>31:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.who.int/campaigns/world-no-tobacco-day\">World No Tobacco Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldNoTobaccoDay</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldTurtleDay&amp;src=typd\"><br />\n</a></strong></p>\n<h2><strong>June</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>5:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.worldenvironmentday.global/\">World Environment Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldEnvironmentDay<br />\n8:\u00a0<a href=\"http://worldoceansday.org/\">World Ocean Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldOceanDay<br />\n12:\u00a0<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_Day_Against_Child_Labour\">World Day Against Child Labour</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldDayAgainstChildLabour</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldOceansDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>14:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.who.int/campaigns/world-blood-donor-day\">World Blood Donor Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldBloodDonorDay<br />\n16: <a href=\"https://www.seaturtleweek.com/world-sea-turtle-day\">World Sea Turtle Day</a> \u2014\u00a0#WorldSeaTurtleDay</strong><br />\n<strong>20:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.unhcr.org/us/get-involved/take-action/world-refugee-day\">World Refugee Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldRefugeeDay<br />\n21:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/yoga-day\">International Day of Yoga</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#YogaDay<br />\n22:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.worldrainforestday.org/\">World Rainforest Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldRainforestDay</strong></p>\n<hr />\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/certificate-programs/certificate-in-artificial-intelligence-ai-for-marketing-fundraising/\">2026 Certificate in Artificial Intelligence (AI) for Marketing &amp; Fundraising program</a> provides an honest, balanced approach to using AI for nonprofit marketing and fundraising\u2014and illuminates why AI literacy is a must-have skill for 2026 and onward. Customized for nonprofit professionals, this webinar series will expand your skill set, advance your career, and help transition your nonprofit into the age of AI.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/certificate-programs/certificate-in-artificial-intelligence-ai-for-marketing-fundraising/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-44090 size-full\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2026-Certificate-in-AI-for-Nonprofits-e1753375936499.png?resize=900%2C707&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"Certificate in AI for Marketing &amp; Fundraising awarded by Nonprofit Tech for Good, signed by CEO Heather Mansfield, with a blue award banner.\" width=\"900\" height=\"707\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2><strong>July</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>11:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/world-population-day\">WorldPopulationDay</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><strong>#WorldPopulationDay</strong><br />\n<strong>18:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.mandeladay.com/\">Nelson Mandela International Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#MandelaDay<br />\n28:</strong>\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https://nationaltoday.com/world-hepatitis-day/\">World Hepatitis Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldHepatitisDay</strong><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Tiger_Day\"><br />\n</a><strong>29: <a href=\"https://www.wwf.org.uk/get-involved/schools/calendar/international-tiger-day\">International Tiger Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#InternationalTigerDay<br />\n30:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/end-human-trafficking-day\">World Day Against Trafficking in Persons</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#EndHumanTrafficking</strong></p>\n<h2><strong>August\u00a0</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>9: <a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/indigenous-day\">Indigenous People&#8217;s Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#IndigenousDay<br />\n10:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.worldanimalprotection.org/our-campaigns/sentience/animal-awareness-days/world-lion-day/\">World Lion Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldLionDay</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/IndigenousDay\"><strong><br />\n</strong></a><strong>12: <a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/youth-day\">International Youth Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#YouthDay</strong><a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/indigenousday/\"><br />\n</a><strong>12:\u00a0<a href=\"http://worldelephantday.org/\">World Elephant Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><strong>#WorldElephantDay</strong><strong><br />\n</strong><strong>17:\u00a0<a href=\"https://nationaldaycalendar.com/days-2/national-nonprofit-day-august-17/\" rel=\"noopener\">National Nonprofit Day</a> \u2014 #NonprofitDay (Internationally recognized)</strong><strong><br />\n19:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.awarenessdays.com/awareness-days-calendar/world-humanitarian-day-2025/\">World Humanitarian Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldHumanitarianDay<br />\n</strong><strong>26: <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Dog_Day\">International Dog Day</a> \u2014\u00a0#DogDay\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldHumanitarianDay\"><br />\n</a>29:\u00a0<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Day_against_Nuclear_Tests\">International Day Against Nuclear Tests</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#AgainstNuclearTestsDay</strong></p>\n<h2><strong>September</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>5:\u00a0<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Day_of_Charity\">International Day of Charity</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#CharityDay<br />\n8:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.unesco.org/en/days/literacy\">International Literacy Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><strong>#LiteracyDay</strong><br />\n<strong>10:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.iasp.info/2024/05/15/worldsuicidepreventionday2024/#:~:text=World%20Suicide%20Prevention%20Day%20is,message%20that%20suicides%20are%20preventable.\">World Suicide Prevention Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><strong>#WorldSuicidePreventionDay<br />\n12:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/world-dolphin-day/\">World Dolphin Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldDolphinDay</strong><br />\n<strong>15:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/democracy-day\">International Day of Democracy</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#DemocracyDay</strong><a href=\"http://www.internationaldayofpeace.org/\"><br />\n</a><strong>21:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/international-day-peace\">International Day of Peace</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#PeaceDay<br />\n</strong><strong>21: <a href=\"https://www.alz.org/about/awareness-initiatives/world-alzheimers-day\">World Alzheimer&#8217;s Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldAlzheimersDay</strong><br />\n<strong>22:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.worldanimalprotection.org/our-campaigns/sentience/animal-awareness-days/world-rhino-day/\">World Rhino Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><strong>#WorldRhinoDay<br />\n27:\u00a0<a href=\"https://nationaltoday.com/world-tourism-day/\">World Tourism Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldTourismDay<br />\n27: <a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/world-rivers-day/\">World Rivers Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldRiversDay</strong><strong><br />\n</strong></p>\n<h2><strong>October</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>4:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.worldanimalday.org.uk/\">World Animal Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><strong>#WorldAnimalDay<br />\n</strong><strong>4</strong><strong>: </strong><strong><a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/habitat-day\">World Habitat Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldHabitatDay</strong><br />\n<strong>5:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.unesco.org/en/days/teachers\">World Teachers Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldTeachersDay<br />\n6</strong><strong>:\u00a0<a href=\"https://worldcpday.org/\">World Cerebral Palsy Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldCPDay</strong><br />\n<strong>10:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.worldhomelessday.org/\">World Homeless Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldHomelessDay<br />\n10:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.who.int/campaigns/world-mental-health-day\">World Mental Health Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><strong>#WorldMentalHealthDay</strong><br />\n<strong>11:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/girl-child-day\">International Day of the Girl Child</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#DayOfTheGirl<br />\n11: <a href=\"https://www.hrc.org/campaigns/national-coming-out-day#coming-out-resources\">Coming Out Day</a></strong> <strong>\u00a0\u2014 #ComingOutDay</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23NCOD\"><br />\n</a><strong>12:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.arthritis.org/about-arthritis/world-arthritis-day\">World Arthritis Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><strong>#WorldArthritisDay<br />\n</strong><strong>13: <a href=\"https://www.worldthrombosisday.org/\">World Thrombosis Day</a> \u2014\u00a0<span class=\"r-18u37iz\">#WorldThrombosisDay<br />\n16:\u00a0<a href=\"https://globalcatday.org/\" rel=\"noopener\">Global Cat Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#GlobalCatDay</span><br />\n</strong><strong>16: <a href=\"http://www.fao.org/world-food-day\">World Food Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldFoodDay<br />\n16: <a href=\"https://www.worldvaluesday.com/\">World Values Day</a> \u2014\u00a0#WorldValuesDay</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldArthritisDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>17: <a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/day-for-eradicating-poverty\">International Day for the Eradication of Poverty</a> \u2014\u00a0#EndPoveryDay<br />\n</strong><strong>29: <a href=\"https://koofr.eu/blog/posts/international-internet-day\">International Internet Day</a> \u2014 #InternetDay\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldInternetDay\"><br />\n</a>31:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/cities-day\">World Cities Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldCitiesDay</strong></p>\n<h2><strong>November</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>3: <a href=\"https://www.unesco.org/en/days/biosphere-reserves\">International Day for Biosphere Reserves</a>\u00a0\u2014 #BiosphereReserves<br />\n13:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.randomactsofkindness.org/world-kindness-day\">World Kindness Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldKindnessDay<br />\n14:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.worlddiabetesday.org/\">World Diabetes Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><strong>#WorldDiabetesDay<br />\n</strong><strong>16: <a href=\"https://www.unesco.org/en/days/tolerance\">International Day for Tolerance</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><strong>#ToleranceDay<br />\n19: <a href=\"https://www.pancreaticcancer.org.uk/get-involved/make-a-difference/pancreatic-cancer-awareness-month-pcam/world-pancreatic-cancer-day/\">World Pancreatic Cancer Day</a> \u2014\u00a0#WorldPancreaticCancerDay</strong><br />\n<strong>19:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.worldtoiletday.info/\">World Toilet Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldToiletDay</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldDiabetesDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>20: <a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/world-childrens-day\">World Children\u2019s Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><strong>#WorldChildrensDay<br />\n20: <a href=\"https://nationaltoday.com/world-philosophy-day/#:~:text=We%20celebrate%20World%20Philosophy%20Day,occurred%20on%20November%2021%2C%202002.\">World Philosophy Day</a> \u2014\u00a0#WorldPhilosophyDay</strong><strong><br />\n</strong><strong>21:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/world-television-day\">World Television Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldTVDay</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23ChildrensDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>25:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/endviolenceday/\">International Day for the Elimination of Violence Against Women</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#EndViolenceAgainstWomen<br />\n</strong></p>\n<h2>December</h2>\n<p><strong>1: <a href=\"http://givingtuesday.org/\">Giving Tuesday</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#GivingTuesday<br />\n1: <a href=\"https://www.unaids.org/en/World_AIDS_Day\">World AIDS Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldAIDSDay<br />\n3:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/day-of-persons-with-disabilities\">International Day of Person with Disabilities</a> \u2014 #IDPwD26</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23IDPWD\"><br />\n</a><strong>5:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/volunteer-day\">International Volunteer Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#VolunteerDay<br />\n5:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/world-soil-day\">World Soil Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#WorldSoilDay</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23IVD2014\"><br />\n</a><strong>9:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/anti-corruption-day\">International Anti-Corruption Day\u00a0</a>\u2014\u00a0#AntiCorruptionDay</strong><a href=\"http://www.worldaidsday.org/\"><br />\n</a><strong>10:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.ohchr.org/en/about-us/human-rights-day\">International Human Rights Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#HumanRightsDay</strong><br />\n<strong>11:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/mountain-day\">International Mountain Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#MountainDay<br />\n18:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/migrants-day\">International Migrants Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0#MigrantsDay</strong></p>\n<hr />\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/certificate-programs/certificate-in-artificial-intelligence-ai-for-marketing-fundraising/\">2026 Certificate in Artificial Intelligence (AI) for Marketing &amp; Fundraising program</a> provides an honest, balanced approach to using AI for nonprofit marketing and fundraising\u2014and illuminates why AI literacy is a must-have skill for 2026 and onward. Customized for nonprofit professionals, this webinar series will expand your skill set, advance your career, and help transition your nonprofit into the age of AI.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/certificate-programs/certificate-in-artificial-intelligence-ai-for-marketing-fundraising/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-44090 size-full\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2026-Certificate-in-AI-for-Nonprofits-e1753375936499.png?resize=900%2C707&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"Certificate in AI for Marketing &amp; Fundraising awarded by Nonprofit Tech for Good, signed by CEO Heather Mansfield, with a blue award banner.\" width=\"900\" height=\"707\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n",
